    <h1>North Star Metric</h1>
    <p class="description">The single number that captures the core value your product delivers to customers. When it grows, the business grows. Companies with a defined NSM grow <strong>2-3x faster</strong> than those without (Amplitude research).</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
